### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Get All Agents
GET http://localhost:3001/api/agents

### Start Agent
POST http://localhost:3001/api/agents/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frontend",
  "role": "フロントエンド開発担当",
  "workDir": "c:/js/test-project",
  "patterns": ["src/**/*.tsx", "src/**/*.ts"]
}

### Get Agent Output
GET http://localhost:3001/api/agents/agent-123/output

### Get All Changes
GET http://localhost:3001/api/changes

### Accept Change
POST http://localhost:3001/api/changes/change-123/accept

### Decline Change
POST http://localhost:3001/api/changes/change-123/decline

### Send Instruction
POST http://localhost:3001/api/changes/change-123/instruction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instruction": "エラーハンドリングを追加してください"
}

### Stop Agent
POST http://localhost:3001/api/agents/stop
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentId": "agent-123"
}
